{"tid":239584,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖 救命 好撚大隻識飛既昆蟲","createTime":"2017-05-11T18:38:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T09:09:49.000Z","uid":7049,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6546b98d8c470b851602d391f155d9e5ff85e0b2","tid":239584,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T18:38:08.000Z","msg":"屌 早一個鐘佢飛撚左入黎 我隻貓隔住玻璃想捉 但之後又消失左 岩岩諗住痾個尿就訓教 屌 發現果隻野係廁所飛緊 佢好少會停低 唔知乜鳩野黎<br />\n嚇撚到我標冷汗<br />\n好想再沖個涼先訓呀屌 有冇方法趕去佢 而家比我鎖左係廁所<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/12/023733_57bdc88ecf4fcb3c01b2d6df726285a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F12%2F023733_57bdc88ecf4fcb3c01b2d6df726285a7.jpg&h=4d45a383&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/12/023740_ec5d81e0edf345d47162c4ed8a22fb3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F12%2F023740_ec5d81e0edf345d47162c4ed8a22fb3a.jpg&h=a36d3d2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n."},{"pid":"34822b75b4263a571ccc4709c6f41600e87aa2b3","tid":239584,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T18:41:02.000Z","msg":"利申 間屋得自己同隻貓 冇得叫老豆趕走佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d7b98b3372e33b60df0471a688af6edb4c7b6d","tid":239584,"uid":15854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T18:41:39.000Z","msg":"電蚊拍"},{"pid":"7170a9fd3b74d05370fcef33740a2b951d8d7463","tid":239584,"uid":91963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T18:41:45.000Z","msg":"都幾得人驚喎<br />\n<br />\n貓唔係不嬲都捉昆蟲嘅咩"},{"pid":"3b2f8e64f4c7825dfdef667ece14ca74495b92db","tid":239584,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T18:43:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都幾得人驚喎<br />\n<br />\n貓唔係不嬲都捉昆蟲嘅咩</blockquote><br />\n係 但今次有玻璃門 佢冇飛到入屋<br />\n琴日隻貓先捉左隻飛蛾<br />\n<br />\n好想去廁所呀<br />\n<br />\n屌仲要